nairātmyādīnām anyatamā prajñā. upāyo hevajraḥ. anayor eva rūpeṇa vidhiniṣpāditena dehadvayasya darśanaparirambhaprativedhavicāraṇāni prajñopāyavidhānam tena pūjayet. tattvavatsala iti tattvasaṃvedanapriyaḥ san.

<commentary>prayatneneti guptau yatnaḥ prayatnaḥ. tam eva āha—yathā bhedo na jāyata iti. bheda udbhedaḥ svayam eva pareṣāṃ yuktibalād abhyūhaḥ. mantrabhedaś ca bhedaḥ. madauddhatyakopādibhiḥ svayaṃ tayā sahāyena vā parasmai kathanaṃ mantrabhedaḥ. 

aguptau narakapātādir adṛṣṭadoṣaḥ prasiddha eva. dṛṣṭadoṣam apy āha—agupta ityādinā. vyāḍādibhiḥ duḥkhaṃ kriyata iti sambandhaḥ. vyāḍāḥ sarpavyāghrādayaḥ. bhūcarāḥ śāsakā narapiśācādayaḥ.</commentary>

mudryate yeneti lakṣyate yataḥ.